<notes>
<note appliesTo="source">line: 39</note>
<note appliesTo="source">prefix: * </note>
</notes>
<segment>
<source>In NVDA 2025.3.3 and 2026.1, additional browse mode elements include frame, graphic, landmark, embedded object, and text paragraph.</source>
</segment>
</unit>
<unit id="5aca8ef2-5445-4da0-9b55-28613a4d7811">
<notes>
<note appliesTo="source">line: 40</note>
<note appliesTo="source">prefix: * </note>
</notes>
<segment>
<source>In NVDA 2026.2 running on a touchscreen computer, additional browse mode elements can be added via NVDA's browse mode settings.</source>
</segment>
</unit>
<unit id="258c5b6d-2565-416b-8f77-b5986aaf2fed">
<notes>
<note appliesTo="source">line: 42</note>
</notes>
<segment>
<source>With scan mode active:</source>
</segment>
</unit>
